structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS
COUNTY GOVERNMENT (FISCAL COURTS AND COUNTY COMMISSIONERS)

law.history: Repealed 1966 Ky. Acts ch. 255, sec. 283. -- Created 1956 Ky. Acts ch. 118, secs. 1 to 4.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Composition of fiscal courts in counties having a population of 75,000 or over; election of commissioners; oath; eligibility.
